PREAMBLE: THE ISLAMIC WAQF (ENDOWMENT)
This software, "Ibad Al-Rahman" (Servants of the Merciful), is developed and released as a "Sadaqah Jariyah" (Continuous Charity) dedicated to the soul of the developer's mother and for the benefit of the entire Muslim Ummah.

By using, modifying, or distributing this software, you acknowledge and agree to the following moral and ethical binding conditions:

1. NON-COMMERCIAL: This software is strictly for non-profit use. It may not be sold, rented, or used as a primary means of generating commercial revenue.
2. NO MONOPOLY: Any derivative work (forks, modifications, updates) must remain Open Source and free for everyone. You cannot close the source code of any project derived from this one.
3. THE SPIRITUAL CURRENCY: The only required "payment" for using this software is a sincere Dua (Supplication) for the original developer and his parents for mercy and forgiveness.

